quran[18]{c,v,t}:
  26,105,Ummanni Nuuh ergamtoota sobsiiftee jirti
  26,106,"Yeroo obboleessi isaanii Nuuh jedheen: “Sila Rabbiin hin sodaattanii"
  26,107,Ani isiniif ergamaa amanamaadha
  26,108,Rabbiin sodaadhaa; ajaja kiyyas fudhaa
  26,109,Ani isa (waamicha kana) irratti mindaa tokkollee isin hin gaafadhu; Mindaan kiyya Gooftaa aalama hundaa irratti malee hin taane
  26,110,Rabbiin sodaadhaaAjaja kiyyas fudhaa.”
  26,111,"[Ummanni isaas] “sila nuti odoo warri gadi aanoon si hordofanii jiranuu siif amannaa?” jedhan"
  26,112,"[Innis] ni jedhe: “Waan isaan dalagaa turan maalittin beeka"
  26,113,Odoo beektanii qormaanni isaanii Gooftaa kiyya qofa irra malee hin taane
  26,114,Ani ari’aa (fageesaa) Mu’uminootaa hin taane
  26,115,Ani akeekkachiisaa ifa bahaa ta’e malee hin taane.”
  26,116,"[Isaan] ni jedhan: “Yaa Nuuh! [waan jettu irraa] yoo dhorgamuu baatte, warra dhakaan cafaqaman irraa taata.”"
  26,117,"[Nuuhis] ni jedhe: “Yaa gooftaa kiyya! Dhugumatti, ummanni koo na sobsiisaniiru"
  26,118,"Ati gidduu kiyyaafi gidduu isaaniitti murtii [haqaa] murteessiAnaafi Mu’uminoota irraa nama na waliin ta’anis baraarsi.”"
  26,119,Nutis isaafi namoota isa waliin turan doonii guutamte keessatti isaan baraarsine
  26,120,"Ergasii booda [bilisa isaan baasuutii] warra hafan ni dhidhimsine"
  26,121,"Dhugumatti, kana keessa mallattootu jiraGaruu irra hedduun isaanii Mu’uminoota hin taane"
  26,122,"Dhugumatti Gooftaan kee Isatu injifataa, rahmata godhaadha"